caption.text:
You didn't really think we forgot your birthday, did you?

It's going going to be a quite long caption, so take a breath first!

The girl whom I met in 9th grade. I had never thought we would be this close. You seemed to fit into any society while I was wondering how to fit in. You were full of laughter yet so smart that I had no idea how to catch up with you!

Remember when they made extra classes with level? You were in a high level and I was in that almost-the-lowest one. Your drawings, your paintings, they were just what I wished I could create. When I found out you had another watty account with a lot of readers and stuffs, I was amazed yet I thought I wasn't cool enough for you.

See the character of Naya in The Newcomer? The multitalented one? That's pretty much like you, but still such a different person.

I should admit that there have been so many things I'm jealous of. But you know what? The jealousy feels just right. Why? Because you are humble, kind and never showing off much. Instead, you give a lot of positive energy and motivation.

Happy birthday! You've been such a great person. May this year bring you more happiness. Meet you soon, yeah?

PS aren't I nice to put that pic instead of the ugly one? Terlihat seperti sedang pundung y.
